%h3 HolacracyOne Badge Holders

Click on any cell to nominate, or view existing nomination.
%br
NEV = Not Enough Votes
%br
LIB = please bring to badge LIBrarian's attention
%br

%table
  %tr
    %td Badge
    - @users.each do |user|
      %td= link_to user.try(:short), user
  - @badges.each do |badge|
    %tr
      %td
        = link_to(badge.name_with_focus, badge)
        %strong
          = ' (' + badge.status + ')' if badge.status && badge.status != 'accepted'
      - @users.each do |user|
        %td= link_to user.badge_level(badge), user.nomination(badge) || new_badge_nomination_path(badge_id: badge.id, user_id: user.id)